%md

## OML4SQL Dimensionality Reduction: SVD

In this notebook, we demonstrate how to use the in-database SVD decomposion for dimensionality reduction.

We use the customer insurance lifetime value data. This dataset contains financial information about the customer and the decision of buying insurance or not. 

We show that Principal Component Analysis can be achieved using SVD results.

OML4SQL Dimensionality Reduction: SVD

In this notebook, we demonstrate how to use the in-database SVD decomposion for dimensionality reduction.

We use the customer insurance lifetime value data. This dataset contains financial information about the customer and the decision of buying insurance or not.

We show that Principal Component Analysis can be achieved using SVD results.

paragraphs.title: Display first two principle components
paragraphs.text:
%sql

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID, FEATURE_VALUE(SVD_CUST_LTV_MDL, 1 USING *) proj1,
    FEATURE_VALUE(SVD_CUST_LTV_MDL, 2 USING *) proj2
FROM CUST_V
ORDER BY 1, 2;
